Then it's some kind of contagion.

858
00:55:12,880 --> 00:55:14,840
<i>Or a virus. Or spores.
I don't know! All right?</i>

859
00:55:14,920 --> 00:55:16,240
I don't know.

860
00:55:16,280 --> 00:55:17,800
But I do know that this
ground's been frozen

861
00:55:17,840 --> 00:55:19,600
for the last 10,000 years.

862
00:55:19,680 --> 00:55:21,040
