on Maxwell's part.

882
00:56:20,200 --> 00:56:23,280
Well, you should know that Motor
is now totally freaking out.

883
00:56:23,360 --> 00:56:24,800
He's taking apart the Snowcat.

884
00:56:24,880 --> 00:56:27,560
What?

885
00:56:27,600 --> 00:56:30,600
Look, we're all under
a lot of pressure out here.

886
00:56:30,640 --> 00:56:32,240
You guys.

887
00:56:34,480 --> 00:56:35,920
You guys, who?

888
00:56:37,080 --> 00:56:41,440
You. And Pollack.

889
00:56:41,520 --> 00:56:43,000
You're perfect for each other.

890
00:56:44,440 --> 00:56:47,200
[door opens, closes]

891
00:56:47,280 --> 00:56:48,840
[beeping]

892
00:56:48,880 --> 00:56:49,800
[taps key]

893
00:56:49,840 --> 00:56:52,720
[bangs key]

894
00:56:54,960 --> 00:56:57,360
I can't email out of here.

895
00:56:57,440 --> 00:56:59,520
You should be packing.

896
00:57:00,720 --> 00:57:01,800
Listen, Elliott,

897
00:57:01,880 --> 00:57:04,040
I want you to come down
to Fairbanks with me.

898
00:57:04,080 --> 00:57:06,920
Staying here's just bullshit.

899
00:57:06,960 --> 00:57:08,240
All right?

900
00:57:08,320 --> 00:57:09,360
And dangerous.

901
00:57:22,920 --> 00:57:25,920
[wind picks up]

902
00:57:28,240 --> 00:57:29,360
<i>[Maxwell, echoing]
Listen. Listen...</i>

903
00:57:31,120 --> 00:57:32,240
<i>Did you see it?</i>

904
00:57:35,800 --> 00:57:36,720
<i>Did you see it?</i>

905
00:57:36,760 --> 00:57:39,040
[stampeding]

906
00:57:39,120 --> 00:57:40,520
<i>[Maxwell, echoing]
They're out there.</i>

907
00:57:40,600 --> 00:57:42,000
<i>Right out there.</i>

908
00:58:01,200 --> 00:58:04,000
[wind blows]

909
00:58:04,080 --> 00:58:05,640
<i>[Maxwell]
Ghosts.</i>

910
00:58:14,680 --> 00:58:17,080
<i>What is oil anyway but fossils?</i>

911
00:58:17,160 --> 00:58:21,880
<i>Plants and animals from...
whatever. Millions of years ago?</i>

912
00:58:27,920 --> 00:58:30,520
<i>We shouldn't be here.</i>

913
00:58:30,600 --> 00:58:31,920
<i>We're grave robbers.</i>

914
00:58:31,960 --> 00:58:34,080
[lights buzz, crackle]

915
00:58:42,520 --> 00:58:45,640
<i>People need to know! Isn't that your Job?</i>

916
00:58:45,680 --> 00:58:47,560
<i>I Just hope this isn't
happening everywhere else.</i>

917
00:59:46,480 --> 00:59:49,640
[no audible dialogue]

918
01:00:01,920 --> 01:00:06,240
[no audible dialogue]

919
01:00:26,560 --> 01:00:28,240
[sobs]

920
01:00:30,160 --> 01:00:32,560
[Ed]
Abby has decided...

921
01:00:32,640 --> 01:00:34,920
