922
01:00:34,960 --> 01:00:37,360
that we should all ship out of here,

923
01:00:37,440 --> 01:00:40,000
and get our heads checked.

924
01:00:40,080 --> 01:00:42,960
I'm gonna second that motion
for the good of the team.

