1030
01:06:33,240 --> 01:06:35,320
That's what we'll do.

1031
01:06:35,400 --> 01:06:38,520
We'll hook up with these guys
and we'll radio for help,

1032
01:06:38,600 --> 01:06:40,440
and we'll have somebody
here by nightfall.

1033
01:06:40,520 --> 01:06:42,120
[James]
I'll go to Fort Crow.

1034
01:06:42,160 --> 01:06:44,440
